        "response_email": "",
        "object": "Сброс пароля",
        "message": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"ru\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\" />\n    <meta http-equiv=\"X-UA-Compatible\" content=\"IE=edge\" />\n    <title>Сброс пароля — RedTail</title>\n    <style>\n        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }\n        body, table, td, a { -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; }\n        table, td { mso-table-lspace: 0pt; mso-table-rspace: 0pt; }\n        img { -ms-interpolation-mode: bicubic; border: 0; outline: none; text-decoration: none; }\n\n        body {\n            background-color: #0f0f11;\n            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Inter', 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;\n            color: #babfba;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n        }\n\n        .email-wrapper {\n            background-color: #0f0f11;\n            padding: 40px 16px 60px;\n        }\n\n        .email-container {\n            max-width: 520px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n\n        .header {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding-bottom: 32px;\n        }\n\n        .brand-name {\n            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Inter', 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;\n            font-size: 28px;\n            font-weight: 300;\n            letter-spacing: 0.22em;\n            text-transform: uppercase;\n            color: #de6161;\n            text-decoration: none;\n        }\n\n        .brand-sub {\n            display: block;\n            font-size: 9px;\n            letter-spacing: 0.22em;\n            text-transform: uppercase;\n            color: #555;\n            margin-top: 4px;\n        }\n\n        .card {\n            background-color: #141416;\n            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.07);\n            border-radius: 16px;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .card-accent {\n            height: 2px;\n            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #de6161, rgba(222, 97, 97, 0.25), transparent);\n        }\n\n        .card-body {\n            padding: 36px 40px 40px;\n        }\n\n        .icon-wrap {\n            width: 52px;\n            height: 52px;\n            border-radius: 14px;\n            background-color: rgba(222, 97, 97, 0.1);\n            border: 1px solid rgba(222, 97, 97, 0.2);\n            margin: 0 auto 28px;\n            display: table;\n        }\n\n        .icon-inner {\n            display: table-cell;\n            text-align: center;\n            vertical-align: middle;\n        }\n\n        .eyebrow {\n            font-size: 9px;\n            font-weight: 700;\n            letter-spacing: 0.28em;\n            text-transform: uppercase;\n            color: #de6161;\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n\n        .heading {\n            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Inter', 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;\n            font-size: 22px;\n            font-weight: 400;\n            letter-spacing: 0.06em;\n            text-transform: uppercase;\n            color: #e8e8e8;\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 12px;\n            line-height: 1.2;\n        }\n\n        .divider-line {\n            width: 32px;\n            height: 1px;\n            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #de6161, transparent);\n            margin: 0 auto 24px;\n        }\n\n        .body-text {\n            font-size: 14px;\n            line-height: 1.75;\n            color: #878787;\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 32px;\n        }\n\n        .body-text strong {\n            color: #babfba;\n            font-weight: 500;\n        }\n\n        .btn-wrap {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 32px;\n        }\n\n        .btn {\n            display: inline-block;\n            padding: 13px 32px;\n            background-color: rgba(222, 97, 97, 0.14);\n            border: 1px solid rgba(222, 97, 97, 0.5);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            color: #e8e8e8 !important;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-size: 12px;\n            font-weight: 700;\n            letter-spacing: 0.14em;\n            text-transform: uppercase;\n        }\n\n        .fallback-wrap {\n            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.025);\n            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            padding: 16px 20px;\n            margin-bottom: 28px;\n        }\n\n        .fallback-label {\n            font-size: 9px;\n            font-weight: 700;\n            letter-spacing: 0.2em;\n            text-transform: uppercase;\n            color: #555;\n            display: block;\n            margin-bottom: 8px;\n        }\n\n        .fallback-url {\n            font-size: 12px;\n            color: #de6161 !important;\n            word-break: break-all;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            line-height: 1.5;\n        }\n\n        .warning-box {\n            background-color: rgba(222, 97, 97, 0.05);\n            border: 1px solid rgba(222, 97, 97, 0.12);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            padding: 14px 18px;\n        }\n\n        .warning-text {\n            font-size: 12px;\n            color: #666;\n            line-height: 1.65;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .warning-text strong {\n            color: rgba(222, 97, 97, 0.7);\n            font-weight: 600;\n        }\n\n        .card-separator {\n            height: 1px;\n            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);\n            margin: 0 40px;\n        }\n\n        .card-footer {\n            padding: 20px 40px 24px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .footer-text {\n            font-size: 11px;\n            color: #444;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            letter-spacing: 0.02em;\n        }\n\n        .footer-text a {\n            color: #555 !important;\n            text-decoration: none;\n        }\n\n        .email-footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding-top: 28px;\n        }\n\n        .email-footer-text {\n            font-size: 10px;\n            letter-spacing: 0.14em;\n            text-transform: uppercase;\n            color: #333;\n        }\n\n        .email-footer-text a {\n            color: #444 !important;\n            text-decoration: none;\n        }\n\n        @media only screen and (max-width: 560px) {\n            .card-body { padding: 28px 24px 32px; }\n            .card-separator { margin: 0 24px; }\n            .card-footer { padding: 16px 24px 20px; }\n            .heading { font-size: 19px; }\n            .email-wrapper { padding: 24px 12px 48px; }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n<div class=\"email-wrapper\">\n    <div class=\"email-container\">\n\n        <div class=\"header\">\n            <h1 class=\"brand-name\">REDTAIL</h1>\n            <span class=\"brand-sub\">Команда переводчиков</span>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"card\">\n            <div class=\"card-accent\"></div>\n\n            <div class=\"card-body\">\n\n                <div class=\"icon-wrap\">\n                    <div class=\"icon-inner\">\n                        🔒\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <p class=\"eyebrow\">Безопасность аккаунта</p>\n                <h1 class=\"heading\">Сброс пароля</h1>\n                <div class=\"divider-line\"></div>\n\n                <p class=\"body-text\">\n                    Мы получили запрос на сброс пароля для вашего аккаунта.<br />\n                    Нажмите кнопку ниже, чтобы задать новый пароль.\n                </p>\n\n                <div class=\"btn-wrap\">\n                    <a href=\"https://redtail.foxgirls.org/auth/reset-password?code=<%= TOKEN %>\" class=\"btn\">\n                        Сбросить пароль →\n                    </a>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"fallback-wrap\">\n                    <span class=\"fallback-label\">Или перейдите по ссылке</span>\n                    <a href=\"https://redtail.foxgirls.org/auth/reset-password?code=<%= TOKEN %>\" class=\"fallback-url\">\n                        https://redtail.foxgirls.org/auth/reset-password?code=<%= TOKEN %>\n                    </a>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"warning-box\">\n                    <p class=\"warning-text\">\n                        <strong>Ссылка действительна 1 час.</strong><br />\n                        Если вы не запрашивали сброс пароля — просто проигнорируйте это письмо. Ваш аккаунт в безопасности.\n                    </p>\n                </div>\n\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"card-separator\"></div>\n\n            <div class=\"card-footer\">\n                <p class=\"footer-text\">\n                    Это автоматическое сообщение от&nbsp;<a href=\"https://redtail.foxgirls.org\">redtail.foxgirls.org</a>.<br />\n                    Пожалуйста, не отвечайте на это письмо.\n                </p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"email-footer\">\n            <p class=\"email-footer-text\">\n                <a href=\"https://redtail.foxgirls.org\">redtail</a>\n                &nbsp;·&nbsp;\n                <a href=\"https://foxgirls.org\">foxgirls.org</a>\n            </p>\n        </div>\n\n    </div>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>"
      }
    },
    "email_confirmation": {
