        "object": "Account confirmation",
        "message": "<p>Thank you for registering!</p>\n\n<p>You have to confirm your email address. Please click on the link below.</p>\n\n<p><%= URL %>?confirmation=<%= CODE %></p>\n\n<p>Thanks.</p>"
      }
    }
